    dc:description "FIGS. 8–16. (8–12) Barbatia diphaeonotus n. sp. (8–11) Holotype, NMW.Z.2001.061.00006: (8) external right valve (MontageTM); (9) external right valve (SEM); (10) internal right valve (SEM); (11) prodissoconch (SEM). (12) Paratype, NMW.Z.2001.061.00009, external left valve (MontageTM). (13) Barbatia elegans, C.305532, Australian Museum, Sydney (photo). (14–16) Barbatia sp., Réunion, NMW.Z.2001.061.00047 (SEM): (14) external right valve; (15) internal right valve; (16) prodissoconch." ;
